</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_145" id="72v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Costäncz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat Peter Volkmeir, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
            lieber <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und ratgesell, als der von
              <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> czu Costencz
            gewesen ist, wol gesagt, wie ir euch gen im gar <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
            beweiset habt, des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ers<ex>amen</ex></expan>
<expan>freunts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz dancken.
            Und biten <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir uns bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>pote<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wissen lassen wöllet, wie ez noch ümb
            sölich leuff und sache bey euch czu Costencz <add>angeslagen,</add> gestalt und gelegen
            sey, ez sey von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> heiligen vater, dem bapst,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigisten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> dem
                <expan>römisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> künig, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> von Osterreich
            und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> so ir eygentlichest mügt,
              <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit das füglich sey. Das
              <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> in <expan>sölch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> oder
                <expan>mer<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
